casebody.data:
Otteburg, Respondent, v. Heather, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County,

General Term.

June 29, 1892.) Appeal from seventh district court. Action by Marcus Otteburg against Henry Heather.

Argued before Bischoff and Giegerich, JJ.

j8. Baker, for appellant. M. Steinert, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment reversed, new trial ordered, costs to appellant to abide the event.
